{"view":"article","slug":"roux-beginner","category":"Roux","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Roux","title":{"zh":"桥式入门教程"},"content":{"zh":"<p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">桥式入门教程</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>1. FB</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"2. SB\">2. SB</span></p></td><td><p><strong>3a. CO</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>3b.CP</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>4a. EO</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>4b. L/R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>4c. EP</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>1. FB (左桥)</strong></p><p>转体让蓝心到左, 可做x转体, 凭直觉转至多2步让白蓝棱到左图位置. <strong>转角: (R U' R' U2)n, n=0,1,2</strong>. *=±1. 称DF和UFR为缓冲. 若角卡在DFL, 做L' U L拿出.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>棱到缓冲</strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong>角到缓冲</strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong>转角</strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong>组对</strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong>插入</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>蓝橙</strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>B </strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>FS (左桥方)</strong></p><p><strong>蓝红到缓冲</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>白蓝橙</p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U2\">M' U2</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>U2 M2</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>r' F</strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> </strong></p><p><strong>FBLP </strong></p><p><strong>(左桥末槽)</strong></p><p><strong>还原白绿</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td><p>白蓝红</p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>U2 M2 U2 </strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>M'</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p> <strong>2. SB (右桥)</strong></p><p>为简化, 以下图形不再画出FB. 白绿棱原地翻公式: <strong>r2 U' r' U' r2</strong>. 可使用的转动: RrMU.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">绿橙</strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U R\">R' U R</span></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> SS (右桥方)</strong></p><p><strong>红绿到缓冲</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>白绿橙</p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>U2 M2</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U2\">M' U2</span></p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U r'\">r U r'</span></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> </strong></p><p><strong>SBLP </strong></p><p><strong>(右桥末槽)</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>白绿红</p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>M'</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image78.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong> </p></td><td></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image80.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>U2 M2 U2</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>最后, 若顶心非白黄, 做M*.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"5\"><p><strong>3a. CO (角色向)</strong></p><p>根据顶面黄格数, 做AUF摆成对应的情况.</p></td><td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong>3b. CP (角序)</strong></p><p>转U层使两个角在左侧归位, 做公式. 若没有, 就在任意方向做公式.<strong> </strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>  0 个</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>  2 个</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>  1 个</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image82.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image84.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image86.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image88.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image90.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image92.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U2' R'\">R U R' U R U2' R'</span></p></td><td></td><td></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U R' F') (R U R' U') (R' F R2 U' R')\">(R U R' F') (R U R' U') (R' F R2 U' R')</span></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>4a. EO (棱色向)</strong></p><p>从这步开始, 所有转动都是MU流. 将所有情况都转化成下面的情况. 紫格表示坏棱, 即顶 (或底) 面非白黄的棱. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image94.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">前箭头</strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image96.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">后箭头</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>尖</strong></p></td><td><p>UF</p></td><td><p>UB</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>翼</strong></p></td><td><p>UL, UR</p></td><td><p>UL,UR</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>底</strong></p></td><td><p>DF</p></td><td><p>DB</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"11\"><p><strong> </strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' r' U' M' U r U r'\">R U' r' U' M' U r U r'</span></p><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image98.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M\">M' U M</span></p></td><td rowspan=\"11\"></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M U M2\">M' U M U M2</span></p></td><td rowspan=\"12\"></td><td rowspan=\"12\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image94.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>M' U* M*</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image96.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>M U* M*</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image100.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>M2</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M U2 M U2 M\">M' U M U2 M U2 M</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M' U2 M U2 M\">M' U M' U2 M U2 M</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image102.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image104.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U2 M' U2\">M' U2 M' U2</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M U2 M' U' M\">M' U M U2 M' U' M</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M U M' U' M\">M' U M U M' U' M</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M U' M' U' M\">M' U M U' M' U' M</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image106.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image108.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image110.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M\">M' U M</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M' U M U' M\">M' U M' U M U' M</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M' U' M U' M\">M' U M' U' M U' M</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image112.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image114.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M'\">M' U M'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>4b. LR (UL/UR棱)</strong></p><p>LR (LR棱, 本教程中是黄蓝和黄绿棱). 用M2, U*, M* U2 M*流先将它们放到DF/DB位置. 藏的第一步是让U层块到D层, 抬 = 让D层块到U层, 平 = 让U (或D) 层块保持在该层, 反M* = 和上一M*相反的M*, 重复M* = 和上一M*相同的M*.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image116.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"4\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image118.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>转U层让角前格</strong></p><p><strong>和FD对色</strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image120.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>M2 U*</strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"3\"></td><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image122.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>LR完成</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td><p><strong>M2</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image124.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image126.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>M2</strong></p></td><td></td><td><p><strong>M* U2, M*藏LR</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>4c. EP (棱序) [非公式22]</strong></p><p><strong>荧光棒</strong></p><p>同色-同色-对色的棱心棱</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image128.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image130.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>以下仅考察M层, 除最后一个分支外, 流程所产生解法最优.</p><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image132.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"图示\n\n描述已自动生成\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/roux-beginner/zh/image133.png\" load